# ✅ .gitignore (FINAL VERSION)

Create `.gitignore` inside **StudentManagementSystem/**:

```gitignore
# Compiled class files
*.class

# Log files
*.log

# Bytecode files
*.jar

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE files (VS Code / IntelliJ)
.vscode/
.idea/

# Output file generated by program
students.dat